[{'type': 'text_link', 'text': '​', 'href': 'https://telegra.ph/file/62d98505393f01879f7ac.jpg'}, {'type': 'bold', 'text': 'Seven new cryptocurrencies start trading on LocalBitcoins

'}, 'LocalBitcoins is adding a number of altcoins, seeing strong demand for them.

The platform for exchanging digital assets between users, LocalBitcoin, adds support for seven more coins. The list includes:

Bitcoin Cash (BCH);
Cardano (ADA)
Chainlink (LINK);
Dogecoin (DOGE);
Polkadot (DOT);
Tether (USDT);
USD Coin (USDC).

LocalBitcoins attribute the expansion to the growing demand for these altcoins. The platform also added to the lists of available payment systems - VODAFONE Cash, PaySera, PAYSEND and others are now at the service of customers.

Not all analysts agree with the high valuation of altcoins. Why some people think Dogcoin is overvalued, read here.']
